Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于我们总是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们被称为"fratello"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"fratello"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是"兄妹"的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由旁人看来或许会觉得可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们确实就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“兄妹”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了掌握共和国派武器来源的重要证人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是得揪出几个据点才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南部的据点就由希尔夏、特莉耶拉兄妹负责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我们没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是另一边…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰、黎可兄妹还需要协助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大楼周边我会和2课的人一起负责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，要与对方接触
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为还需要一组兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰？我是希尔夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经压制住了共和国派的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没发现重要证人的踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他大概已经被移送到你们那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出证据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会找看看有没有人还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见吗？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔瑟，你做得来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长，我认为他们还无法参与团体行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的，约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰、黎可兄妹就和乔瑟、亨莉耶塔兄妹一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧，约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到特莉耶拉、希尔夏兄妹的联络
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们这里才是真正的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先确定那个重要证人是否和他们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法确定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先观察他们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛，出入口没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面有我跟亚鲁法松
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方则有阿马迪欧和乔窍看着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方要逃也只剩那扇窗户可跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静候指示了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎可，注意百叶窗的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南部的据点被抄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有人正在找那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这里不也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许会过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说出现在据点的是个年幼的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我曾听过一个传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个组织专门雇佣少女当杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易，是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个穿西装的男人，还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个…女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来把他们赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易，不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉上门打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我是杂志《自由意大利》的记者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记者来这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说科斯蒂罗公司的斯卡罗先生在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能采访他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没你说的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找错地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确听说他就住在这栋大楼里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都跟你说没这个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你没听见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有你说的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好识相点，不然我就会给你好看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算跑遍全意大利的医院吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥，真的非得要小孩子不可吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公社的人是那么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是改造身体还是接受制约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说年纪越小越好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是社会福利公社的人，对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家真是设立了一个不错的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然这么积极地参与紧急医疗支援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛琪医师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是听说这间医院有位受重伤的少女才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她极需你们的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是上星期灭门血案的唯一幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在家人的尸体旁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整晚惨遭蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本人业已毫无求生意志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要帮她取什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨莉耶塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨莉耶塔…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先让她住单人房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到熟悉了这里之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让她与黎可住双人房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得渴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫乔瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经起床了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您希望我能早点学会操作这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战射击时不要使用瞄准镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要视地形环境来掌控目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是近距离你就得像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将子弹射入人体中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能够命中此处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能封锁住对方的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差强人意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手榴弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛，行动失败
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带几个人过来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨莉耶塔，你为什么会突然失去理智？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从未这样过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手臂中弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲洛，找出那个重要证人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他们的反应看来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人一定就藏在这栋建筑物之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚鲁法松，阿马迪欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们从屋顶开始往下搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔窍负责建筑物的周边戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪，别对我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是应该让她接受彻底的制约才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎犬终究还是需要项圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥，我反对这点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断让她接受制约会缩短她的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去找新的病患不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太爱护工具了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰，你先等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然存在一些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但亨莉耶塔确实很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随随便便就舍弃她未免可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我们也找到了那位重要证人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事你就睁一只眼闭一只眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样处理义体全凭其担当官一人决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你说只对亨莉耶塔进行最低限度的制约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这么试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能再犯下严重的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事，你一定要好好训诫她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初带亨莉耶塔到公社的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个话很少的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她原本就是连续杀人事件的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会这样也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家六口惨遭杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩她一人幸存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在国立医院见到她时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身心都已遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选择了这女孩作为伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道这是为了积人品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是出自同情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，我就是很想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨莉耶塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎可都跟我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你大闹了一场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一时气昏头…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特莉耶拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吧，你来我和库拉耶斯的房间来喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝一杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红茶和蛋糕里有着让人幸福的魔法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你只是急于立功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，特莉耶拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做的也只有这么多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人甘愿为我如此奉献、牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只会觉得烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口开始痛了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想帮您的忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之后，你马上去让医生治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回“观星”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


